</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0186-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0186-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0101" class="document">Hall to GW, 1 June 1757</a>, and notes.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0186-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0186-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>The word revolution is used here in the sense of passage or lapse of time.</p>

